sheet.description:
You can affix spikes to a set of nonmagical armor during a rest with smith's tools, turning it into Spiked Armor. When worn by you:
It counts as a martial melee weapon with 5 ft. range, dealing 1d4 + {{strength:modifier}} piercing damage;
When Raging, you can use a bonus action to make a Spiked Armor attack;
When you successfully grappe, the target also takes 1d4 piercing damage

